headline.main: DAVIES AT MINNEAPOLIS; The President's Envoy to Stalin Completes Another Leg

lead_paragraph: MINNEAPOLIS, June 2 (AP) -Joseph E. Davies, President Roosevelt's emissary to Premier Joseph Stalin of the Soviet Union, arrived here late today by plane en route to Washington. 1VIr. Davies came here from Seattle on an Army bomber and was taken to a downtown hotel, where he planned to spend the night_ He declined to make any statement to newspapermen. T-y.j. journey will be resumed tomorrow.
